  "description": {
    "zh": "雇佣兵，我还有一些任务需要你完成。希望 Skier 没让你头疼太久。\n\n这次我要你用某些西方突击步枪证明你的实力。别想着我会借给你武器——它们太贵了，所以你得自己想办法弄到手。\n\n任何西方制造的突击步枪都可以，但这次的难点在于数量。这任务不会很快结束，你需要击杀你看到的任何人，不管是谁，甚至包括 USEC。目前他们对我们没什么重要性，而且大多数干员已经叛逃了。\n\n怎么样，能胜任吗？完成后记得向我汇报。",
    "en": "Well then mercenary, I still have a few tasks for you left. I hope that Skier did not cause you too big of a headache.\n\nI want you to prove your skills with certain western rifles, and don't think I will lend you some, they are expensive so you are on your own with getting your hands on them.\nAny Western-Made Assault rifle will do just fine for this job, however the twist here is not the task itself but the quantity. Don't think this will be over quick, get rid of anyone you see, doesn't matter who, hell even USECs. There aren't of any importance for us at the moment, besides most operators have gone rogue anyway.\n\nIs that something you can be trusted with? Report back to me when you are finished."
  },
